data.description: Discover this hidden gem nestled in a charming cul-de-sac. This 4 bedroom and 4.5 bath home is close to eateries, highways, banks, and shopping. This home has coffered ceiling in the dining room, hardwood stairs with wrought iron railing, and inviting arch entryways. A spacious, gourmet kitchen with an oversize island that seamlessly flows into the family room with a cozy fireplace. Home has been freshly painted and new carpet throughout for a refreshed look. This home has a enormous owner's suite with a sitting room and 2 huge closets. The secondary bedrooms are big with their own bathrooms! Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home!
